thread.title: Kevin

author: Kevin
title: Kevin
text:
Purchase was smooth, communication was good, fast delivery, no problem with the transaction. Item is good quality and is now in constant use by 3,4,20 and 51 year olds....
The island takes a lot of assembly so don't expect a straight out of the box expiriance the instructions say 30 to 40 minutes but if you want to get the stickers right I'd say put another 30 on that...
I never bought this type of toy before and I have to say it's been a good experience...
